  <h1>What Is a Good ATS Score? (2026 Guide)</h1>
  <div class="meta">Updated April 2026 · 10 min read</div>

  <p><strong>A good ATS score is 80 or above out of 100.</strong> Scores above 80 mean your resume will pass most automated screening filters and reach a human recruiter. Below 70, you're likely being auto-rejected.</p>

